  level: Level 4
  name: Scalars & Vectors
  description: Scalars are quantities with just a value, while vectors have both
    value and direction.
  quizItems:
  - rid: 7832858353301979137
  - rid: 7832858353301979138
  - rid: 7832858353301979139
  - rid: 7832858353301979141
